{"type":"message","id":"d6e47273","parentId":"c1698d76","timestamp":"2026-04-02T03:49:38.171Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"只有一个session，这是当前cron任务自身的session，不是活跃的用户对话。我需要检测是否有真实的用户对话，而不是这个cron任务本身。\n\n让我查询更广泛一些，看看是否有其他活跃的对话，排除当前的cron session。\n\n实际上，从返回结果来看：\n- 只有1个session\n- 这个session的key是 `agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978`\n- 这就是当前cron任务自己的session\n\n所以实际上没有活跃的用户对话。不过我应该再检查一下是否有其他session，或者看看session的lastChannel是什么。\n\n等等，这个cron任务是作为 agent:main 运行的，lastChannel是webchat，这可能是通过网页界面与用户交互的session。让我再仔细看一下：\n\n- key: \"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978\" - 这是cron触发的agent:main session\n- kind: \"other\" - 不是user session\n- label: \"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习\" - 这是这个cron任务自己的label\n\nmessages里只有一条assistant消息（就是刚才调用sessions_list的那条），说明这是cron任务刚启动，没有真实的用户消息。\n\n不过，我需要更仔细地判断。让我看看updatedAt时间：\n- updatedAt: 1775101760757\n\n\n- 换算成北京时间大约是2026-04-02 11:49:20\n\n而当前时间是 2026-04-02 11:49 AM (Asia/Shanghai)，所以这个session确实是在最近5分钟内的。但这是cron任务自己的session，不是真实的用户对话。我需要更智能地判断。\n\n看messages数组，只有一条工具调用消息，没有user消息进来过。真正的用户对话应该有user role的消息。所以结论是：没有活跃的用户对话，应该执行自主学习。","thinkingSignature":"9e12102068c935d354895f4897d8b762549f27b83547f7878114be6af05385b8"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到只有一个session且是cron任务自身的session（只有assistant消息，没有user消息），判断为**无活跃用户对话**，执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_niaxy9vm9tku_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":845,"output":449,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45275,"cost":{"input":0.0002535,"output":0.0005388,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00211173}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775101766380}}
{"type":"message","id":"35133f0d","parentId":"d6e47273","timestamp":"2026-04-02T03:49:38.177Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_niaxy9vm9tku_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775101778174}}
{"type":"message","id":"59a8a2df","parentId":"35133f0d","timestamp":"2026-04-02T03:49:44.019Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态。让我并行搜索几个关键词。","thinkingSignature":"6f507a3c2bbae59d03e4a264597cbcff37ae298d822cb53af02f73fb54d4cf4f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_chg9gbgo7zvd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型最新政策 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -c 5000"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_chg9gbgo7zvd_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -c 5000"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_chg9gbgo7zvd_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成行业发展趋势 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -c 5000"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_chg9gbgo7zvd_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务行业趋势 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -c 5000"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1809,"output":243,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46033,"cost":{"input":0.0005427,"output":0.0002916,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00215373}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775101778177}}
